{"tid":2173240,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"內媒重提鄧小平孫做鎮官　迴避媒體不願有特寫鏡頭","createTime":"2020-08-25T06:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T07:00:54.000Z","uid":120499,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c80b463b19929e1c1e2181065f979c2101303d7b","tid":2173240,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200824/mobile/bkn-20200824094547468-0824_00952_001.html#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200824%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200824094547468-0824_00952_001.html%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D1&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXT632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=73ec875d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200824/mobile/bkn-20200824094547468-0824_00952_001.html#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1</a><br />\n<br />\n周三（26日）是深圳經濟特區建立40周年紀念日，內媒周日（23日）報道，重提已故中共領導人鄧小平唯一孫兒鄧卓棣，被指是「鄧家唯一從政第3代」。他於早年5月曾在廣西百色市平果縣新安鎮三合村龍懷屯里擔任3天屯長，屯是村下一級的村民小組，是中國農村社會最小一級的組織。內媒表示，鄧卓棣刻意迴避媒體，不願在當地電視新聞報道上出現自己的特寫鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，現年33歲的鄧卓棣在<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">美國出生</span></span>，2007年從北京大學畢業後，到<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">美國杜克大學學習1年，獲得法學碩士學位，獲聘於美國偉凱律師事務所（White &amp; Case）</span></span>。鄧小平的大女兒鄧林曾表示，「小弟兒（鄧卓棣）是最小的孫子，是爺爺的心尖兒」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，鄧卓棣2013年5月到任廣西平果縣後，首次出現在公開媒體上，惟回響太大，隨後均用「該鎮黨委書記」代稱。鄧卓棣曾於2013至2014年開始擔任新安鎮黨委書記和平果縣委副書記，直到2016年不再擔任相關職務。<br />\n鄧卓棣在新安鎮引進一項路燈修建項目&mdash;從鎮政府到廣昆高速之間的二級公路段修建路燈，長約4公里；又解決新安鎮三合村的學校沒有圍牆的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y39Xkoc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy39Xkoc.png&h=69ed577c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅三代已經要開始接管支共政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n權力傳承<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80373553fb7088d5cf62b93ded86553300e65a4f","tid":2173240,"uid":156130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T06:48:01.000Z","msg":"解決新安鎮三合村的學校沒有圍牆的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好難解決咩？？"},{"pid":"7df79ec54c98cb3394e2d72b3a73fdb56ee785a0","tid":2173240,"uid":98915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80373553fb7088d5cf62b93ded86553300e65a4f","tid":2173240,"uid":156130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T06:48:01.000Z","msg":"解決新安鎮三合村的學校沒有圍牆的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好難解決咩？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"好難架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰啲地方有鞋著已經俾面你<br />\n依家有幅牆俾你 啲小學生要跪係度幫領導啜龍汁架"}]}